it then success). No dependence on model output quality. Rejected System because behavior text does not require real network timing/pathologies, only correct wait-and-retry control flow.","test_description":"Use fake API client scripted to return rate-limit error first then success; assert module performs delay/backoff, retries expected number of times, and returns successful label instead of bubbling immediate error.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.06,"Integration":0.76,"System":0.16,"Agentic":0.02,"Workflow":0.0}}]}
